{"hae9d0f96g5d0eg4c7dgacbfg1318c45a8385": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "f6d7f741-5bd4-4aab-bb8b-fd7aa903f0c8"], "hfc09ec57g0961g4126ga8bag120a25156ccc": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "daa19c5d-650f-4da6-880f-7bdd4ac6a071"], "hfbc6a9a9gfc4cg490dgb37dgab6e3b2e0fee": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "de3bb1ac-1ede-48a9-bb7c-d95b7b337961"], "h305a4b8bgf67dg46e0g8f8bgf1f55ae5462e": ["What's your name?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "e93b010a-4204-4df0-82e2-234c7efdda9d"], "h5948005egd89eg4f62g9142g930fe5fd3aaf": ["Rolan. Just... Rolan.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "ce3bec01-6f12-4205-9577-5c8a050f9072"], "he29bc3e8g033bg4fd1g84eag92ca26d90537": ["Do you have any family?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "66444ae8-f0b0-982e-79d7-a1ffa83eaf31"], "hbb33fd73g749fg4575ga78egdbcd52e2decc": ["No... family... no one.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "e6c6cb04-ef94-3cff-5194-53fbdd4fb7a9"], "h828b7bcegc45ag4fd0g8f20gc97c0418dbf8": ["No family? What about Lia and Cal?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "e1ed81c0-3332-057d-3a3e-ff9abfd7259e"], "hca15ce36gdb56g43a6gb93eg26acc871c9e4": ["They are... brother and sister. Cal says... I am family, but...", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "0b7a42f8-ed74-e20b-6a05-902c771fdc7d"], "hec241514gad4eg48bfgb9dcg28cc5af209f7": ["Did you come here alone?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "8d6cbdee-90c4-17dd-86a8-6ad1fc8930e9"], "h0bd59878g2771g43e5g9048g9e3f63219cbc": ["With Lia... and Cal. They are brother and sister. But I am... not blood.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "3c389c2f-4ee7-f5fa-31a5-0294e6444896"], "h33fd0b26g6a4fg4c9dg8e20g33d0324ba870": ["How did you die?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "a5f6bf32-66d2-4912-a306-bf06cc093eae"], "he9787f71gf713g41ceg81d0g28eaf4d73c89": ["Too fast but... can't be. Must finish...", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "edab6983-d9a3-49b9-8a22-028b30f96d40"], "h6f6c46a8g4e42g4dcegb727g65aff3f4fc69": ["Finish what?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "6f12bac5-e237-0047-c33d-24c93d129ee7"], "h559c0e1fga4dcg47dcg9061gbbf2cb596945": ["My... training... must get to... Lorroakan.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "16105011-de34-3427-ab88-93f70ed36587"], "h03d93ef3g0178g4ca2g8279ge9c1ead863e8": ["Where are you from? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "09615ec0-8f3f-47cb-b668-950c63fd900c"], "hbd8d51c6gfb06g4624gb3edgc97d3c2eec02": ["The city that... survived Hell.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "ace84856-d21b-4d98-a153-96dcf04d6124"], "h625beabbgbd4eg4309g80d3g67c501072ccf": ["Where were you going?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "14d7155c-31a3-478b-a229-7eff0e1cc99b"], "h38166df9g60d9g4681g94bege238030764c9": ["To Baldur's Gate... to Lorroakan... my destiny.", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "4799a31c-ea19-4557-9f57-d76f798ecee6"], "h531d1cbbg1bbfg47efgb24cgb634e644ac8e": ["What is so important about Lorroakan?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "2986bdec-3f1f-e841-35e7-b29396f83560"], "h9697c2d6g52bcg45f7g8f36g9c1acaea826d": ["<i>Everything. </i>He'll make me... greatest wizard... in Faer\u00fbn. ", "b6a3a9e9-b6eb-4c19-ab3f-4c431178fe1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "344ff707-8a67-ee7d-5c39-0f397b8a7b97"], "hf6733d0egf48bg4566gb720g236fcdfedbe6": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "17072780-9d00-45ac-b457-cbf8a79859b6"], "he4d2154dg6f88g46e1g9781g2657208428e9": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Prodigy_Dead.html", "eed0c286-64cf-4fb1-a26e-fb06ecbaa94a"]}